[Margaret retching]

1377
01:29:54,207 --> 01:29:55,247
[Margaret coughs]

1378
01:29:55,382 --> 01:29:56,576
Margaret.

1379
01:29:56,712 --> 01:29:58,482
- [coughing]
- [♪ suspenseful music plays]

1380
01:29:58,618 --> 01:30:00,754
[heavy breathing]

1381
01:30:01,655 --> 01:30:03,257
