1382
01:30:03,392 --> 01:30:05,121
[breath trembling]

1383
01:30:07,461 --> 01:30:08,729
[tires skid]

1384
01:30:29,619 --> 01:30:31,446
[glass shards clattering]

1385
01:30:33,958 --> 01:30:37,023
