1434
01:34:41,744 --> 01:34:43,745
The very first moment we met,

1435
01:34:43,880 --> 01:34:45,417
do you remember
what I said to you?

1436
01:34:46,823 --> 01:34:47,957
That you, Margaret,

1437
01:34:48,093 --> 01:34:51,258
