I'd ever known.

1438
01:34:52,162 --> 01:34:55,628
Now you know how special
you are to me.

1439
01:34:55,764 --> 01:34:56,765
To us.

1440
01:34:56,833 --> 01:34:58,995
[shackles rattle]

1441
01:34:59,131 --> 01:35:03,699
The baby you're about to bear
