1535
01:42:48,064 --> 01:42:49,464
Don't we?

1536
01:42:51,564 --> 01:42:54,102
[breathes heavily]

1537
01:42:54,238 --> 01:42:56,604
You did so well, my child.

1538
01:42:59,276 --> 01:43:01,576
[breathing heavily]

1539
01:43:03,415 --> 01:43:06,149
